Sentencas: Ni-(Y2O3)(0.08)(ZrO2)(0.92)(YSZ) anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell (HF-SOFC) with an outer diameter of 1.1 mm was successfully fabricated by a wet spinning/sintering process.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The anode-supported hollow fiber shows a highly asymmetric structure with finger-like voids at the inner side and sponge-like pores at the outer side.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Dense YSZ electrolyte layer about 6.5 mu m was deposited onto the anode hollow fiber by dip coating.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-delta (LSM)-YSZ was acted as the composite cathode.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance of the as-prepared HF-SOFC was tested at 650-800 degrees C with humidified H-2 as fuel and ambient air as oxidant, respectively.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cell provides maximum power densities of 285, 446, 549 and 708 mW cm(-2) at 650, 700, 750 and 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C, the fuel utilization of the maximum power output with different fuel flow rate has been calculated.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The excellent performance of the cell indicates that the HF-SOFC has great potential applications in auxiliary power units (APUs) and power sources of portable devices.
Titulo: Novel asymmetric anode-supported hollow fiber solid oxide fuel cell
